    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model predicts RH < 1 across all five CPB operating points with a maximum discrepancy of 18.3% against experimental data, within the 25% acceptance threshold. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device. The model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions.",
